前奥兹·奥斯本吉他手杰克·E·李在拉斯维加斯多次枪击https://www.nme.com/news/music/former-ozzy-osbourne-guitarist-jake-e-lee-shot-multiple-times-in-las-vegas-3803132?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=former-奥兹·奥斯本吉他手杰克·e·李在拉斯维加斯多次射击Surej SinghWed, 16 Oct 2024 02:23:05 +0000 Music NewsNewsMetalRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3803132 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ozzy-jake-e-lee@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="奥兹·奥斯本和杰克·E·李在舞台上现场表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ozzy-jake-e-lee@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ozzy-jake-e-lee@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ozzy-jake-e-lee@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ozzy-jake-e-lee@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ozzy-jake-e-lee@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ozzy-jake-e-lee@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>预计他将“完全康复”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/former-ozzy-osbourne-guitarist-jake-e-lee-shot-multiple-times-in-las-vegas-3803132">前 Ozzy Osbourne 吉他手 Jake E. Lee 在拉斯维加斯多次拍摄的</a>照片首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ozzy-jake-e-lee@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="奥兹·奥斯本和杰克·E·李在舞台上现场表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ozzy-jake-e-lee@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ozzy-jake-e-lee@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ozzy-jake-e-lee@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ozzy-jake-e-lee@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ozzy-jake-e-lee@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/ozzy-jake-e-lee@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>杰克·E·李 (Jake E. Lee) 是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ozzy-osbourne">奥兹·奥斯本 (Ozzy Osbourne)</a>的前吉他手，他在拉斯维加斯多次遭到枪击 - 请在下面了解有关该事件的更多信息。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <strong><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/ozzy-osbourne-tour-retirement-black-sabbath-3390656">奥兹·奥斯本（Ozzy Osbourne）：无与伦比的摇滚表演者</a></strong></li></ul><p>根据<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/jake-e-lee-ozzy-osbourne-badlands-shot-1235134450/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《滚石》杂志</em></a>吉他手代表分享的一份声明，枪击事件发生在周二凌晨（10 月 15 日）。虽然尚不清楚李中枪了多少次，但该代表告诉<em>《滚石》杂志</em>，他将“完全康复”。</p><p>除了地方当局正在调查该事件并且他们认为枪击事件“完全是随机的”外，有关该事件的信息几乎没有被分享。</p><p>声明中写道：“李在拉斯维加斯一家医院的重症监护室里意识清醒，状况良好。预计他将完全康复。拉斯维加斯当局认为这起枪击事件完全是随机的，发生在李凌晨带着他的狗出去散步时。由于事件正在调查中，警方不会发表进一步评论。李和他的家人此时非常感谢尊重他们的隐私。” </p><figure id="attachment_3803133" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3803133" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3803133" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/jake-e-lee@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/jake-e-lee@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/jake-e-lee@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/jake-e-lee@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/jake-e-lee@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/jake-e-lee@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/jake-e-lee@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3803133" class="wp-caption-text">杰克·E·李.图片来源：Larry Busacca/WireImage</figcaption></figure><p>拉斯维加斯大都会警察局发言人也向<em>滚石杂志</em>证实，“目前尚未逮捕任何人”。</p><p>奥兹·奥斯本 (Ozzy Osbourne) 对李被枪杀的消息做出了反应，他告诉<a href="https://www.tmz.com/2024/10/15/ozzy-osbourne-guitarist-jake-e-lee-shot-las-vegas/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>TMZ</em></a> ：“我已经 37 年没有见过杰克·E·李了，但这仍然无法消除今天听到他发生的事情时的震惊。这只是又一起毫无意义的枪支暴力行为。我向他和他美丽的女儿杰德表达了我的思念。我只是希望他一切都好。”</p><p> 1982 年至 1987 年间，Jake E. Lee 是 Ozzy Osbourne 独奏乐队的一员，在此期间，他与 Price of Darkness 录制了两张专辑，并进行了多次巡演。离开奥斯本的项目后，李在几个乐队以及他自己的独奏项目中担任吉他手。</p><p>其他新闻方面，最近宣布演员兼<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Tenacious-D">Tenacious D</a>主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Jack-Black">杰克·布莱克 (Jack Black)</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jack-black-to-induct-ozzy-osbourne-into-rock-and-roll-hall-of-fame-3799511">今年将邀请这位“疯狂火车”歌手进入摇滚名人堂</a>。这将标志着奥斯本第二次入选，第一次是他在 2006 年作为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Black-Sabbath">黑色安息日</a>成员所做的工作。</p><p>为纪念这位歌手的独唱生涯， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Billy-Idol">Billy Idol</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Tool">Tool 乐队</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Maynard-James-Keenan">Maynard James Keenan</a>和乡村艺术家 Jelly Roll 等人也将在活动中表演 Osbourne 的歌曲。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/former-ozzy-osbourne-guitarist-jake-e-lee-shot-multiple-times-in-las-vegas-3803132">前 Ozzy Osbourne 吉他手 Jake E. Lee 在拉斯维加斯多次拍摄的</a>照片首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
